    "Two-step cleanup for memories, user profile blocks, and skill files. Scan first, review every candidate, then archive and erase only checked items.": {
      "extractionState": "extracted",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Two-step cleanup for memories, user profile blocks, and skill files. Scan first, review every candidate, then archive and erase only checked items."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Nettoyage en deux étapes pour les mémoires, les blocs de profil utilisateur et les fichiers de skills. Analysez d’abord, examinez chaque candidat, puis archivez et effacez uniquement les éléments cochés."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Limpieza en dos pasos para memorias, bloques del perfil de usuario y archivos de habilidades. Escanea primero, revisa cada candidato y luego archiva y borra solo los elementos marcados."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Zweistufige Bereinigung für Erinnerungen, Benutzerprofilblöcke und Skill-Dateien. Zuerst scannen, jeden Kandidaten prüfen und dann nur markierte Elemente archivieren und löschen."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "对记忆、用户配置文件块和技能文件进行两步清理。先扫描，审查每个候选项，然后仅归档并擦除已勾选的项目。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
